kuusisto.tinysound.internal

Class ByteList

  • java.lang.Object
    • kuusisto.tinysound.internal.ByteList

  • public class ByteList
extends Object
    The ByteList class is a dynamically sized array of primitive bytes. This allows the use of a dynamically sized array without the extra overhead that comes with List\. ByteList is an internal class of the TinySound system and should be of no real concern to the average user of TinySound.
    Author:
    Finn Kuusisto
